data.description: Beautifully remodeled home in the heart of Sandy, w/gorgeous hardwood floors on the main level, open concept, upgraded kitchen w/granite counter tops, lots of cabinets for storage, an amazing deck that opens up to a yard fully manicured w/mature trees with lots a space to entertain or just enjoy a night out on the deck, New fresh neutral paint, spacious 4 beds, 3 bath, a family room upstairs/downstairs for entertaining. New roof will be done at the end of January. Close to skiing, shopping, transportation, this home offers so much and checks all the boxes. Owner has taken pride in keeping it immaculate and up to date!  Come see this beautiful home and make it yours today!
